        <div class="content text" id="about-content">
            I am a senior at Georgia Tech pursuing a B.S. in Computer Science with the Platform and Information Internetworking threads.
            I plan on graduating in December of 2013, and I will be returning to RetailMeNot as an Associate Software Engineer after graduation.
            I hope to work with like-minded individuals who can work together as a team and teach each other as we face new challenges.
            My ideal work environment consists of a company that can provide me with a enjoyable and open workplace,
                coworkers who share my passion for creating things,
                and opportunities to work on projects that people will use, enjoy, and benefit from.
            <br /><br />
            Subsets of software engineering that I am interested in include, but are not limited to:
                <ul>    
                    <li>Mobile Development</li>
                    <li>Web Development</li>
		    <li>Back-End Developer</li>
                    <li>Penetrating Testing</li>
                    <li>Operating System Development</li>
                </ul>
            <br />
            My biggest accomplishment to date was my work with RetailMeNot (formerly know as WhaleShark Media) on their RetailMeNot Android app.
            As half of a two-person team, I helped create an Android app that currently has between 1,000,000 and 5,000,000 downloads.
            Go check it out on the 
            <a class="bold" href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.whaleshark.retailmenot&hl=en">Play Store.</a>
